Happy Autism Acceptance Month! April 1st kicks off our nationwide fundraising campaign with our partners at @getairsports! When you go to your nearest @getairsports trampoline park this April, your visit will help people and families affected by autism. We are so thankful to have such an amazing partner who is so committed to autism acceptance and inclusion for all! Kick off April with a jump start and find a Get Air Trampoline Park near you to visit with your friends and family!

When you visit any Get Air Trampoline Park during April, you can make a donation to the Flutie Foundation at the cash registers or when you buy socks to jump. All funds raised will go directly to help people with autism be included, respected and engaged in their communities!

Thank you, @getairsports, for your continued and generous support in the autism community. Let's GO!!!
